title: The Garin Collection, v2.0
description:
A biger and better collection of all of Garin's 40K .stl files, snagged before GW dropped the C&D. Also contains files from other GW models on thingiverse and other relevant .stl files.

v2.0, as of 11/3/2013

Contains the following:

Apocalypse
-Knight Paladin Titan
-Tyranid Bio-Titan

Variety of city and ship corridor bases

Imperial Guard:
-Leman Russ tank
-Sentinel

Necrons:
-Monolith

Orks:
-Orks
-Orc conversion kit for other models
-Grotzooka and Deffkopta Bigbomb

Space Marines:
-Various Torsoes, bodies, and arms/legs
-Various weapons
-Bikes, and bike-riding models
-Dreadnoughts (Model and weapon options)
-Drop pods
-Grek Knight Terminator captain
-Various Primarchs
-Terminators and weapon options
-Centurions w/50mm bases
-One-piece marines
-Female marines (One-piece)

Tau
-Drone body

Tyranids:
-Termagaunts
-Carnifex
-Zoanthrope
-Hive Tyrant
-Tervigon

Enjoy, and fuck GW!
